{
  "stem": "22889.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, all those years where I spent in camp you loose faith, let's face it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not the only one I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Majority of us, how could there be God?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where is the God?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What happens to us?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But always I thought to myself, I was praying every night before I went to sleep if I-- and I had such a tremendous will to live.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want to live so bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't want to die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to become a Muslim or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I want to find this man someday-- come later on to the story what happened to me, coming to the United States.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I work for him for about-- about four months maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then I was assigned to different-- in 1940 I was assigned to work in a stone quarry in a small town not to far from my hometown called Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Zakopane is resort town, a small town. 1938 it were the Winter Olympics in this little town, Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when we were children, when we were kids at home, we used to hike, you know, from-- from the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Early in the morning we start to hike from our hometown to Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next day, my uncle-- I had-- I had relatives in Zakopane [INAUDIBLE] used to bring us back home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I work-- I was assigned to work in the stone quarry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were quite a few because don't forget we were in business, and we'd been in business for a long time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody knew my family, especially my mother's side family, Mendlers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were very famous in town, you know, not because we weren't millionaires.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
